name: Common Names from the Cataologue of Life, 2019 annual release
description: This file consists of a (bz2-compressed) tsv table of common names extracted from the Darwin Core Archive version of the 2019 release of the Catalogue of Life, http://www.catalogueoflife.org/DCA_Export/zip-fixed/2019-annual.zip. Data has been cleaned/processed using an R script https://github.com/cboettig/taxadb/blob/c4c98953247f49f971823a3e27b0200638bd552b/data-raw/col.R.  Note that the ID of the data download is the sha-256 sum of the uncompressed data file, following hash-uri conventions.
